ActFood and Drugs Act
SubjectInterim Order Respecting the Importation, Sale and Advertising of Drugs for Use in Relation to COVID-19
PrecisOrder approving the INTERIM ORDER RESPECTING THE IMPORTATION, SALE AND ADVERTISING OF DRUGS FOR USE IN RELATION TO COVID-19, made by the Minister of Health on September 16, 2020 in order to allow the issuance of an expedited authorization for the importation, sale and advertising of drugs used in relation to COVID-19.
